08:57.600 --> 09:00.068
We're going to
the best vegetarian restaurant in town.

09:00.800 --> 09:02.677
Oh, boy.

09:14.400 --> 09:16.755
Oh, thank God. Meat.

09:16.920 --> 09:20.117
-l love you, Rose.
-l love you too, Charlie.

09:20.280 --> 09:23.397
And may l say, l would never
try to change you the way she has.

09:23.920 --> 09:26.275
-Her name's Mia.
-l know what her name is.

09:26.440 --> 09:28.908
l also know where she lives,
her employment history. . .

09:29.080 --> 09:32.470
. . .and if you want l can get you
photographs of a wet T-shirt contest. . .

09:32.640 --> 09:38.158
. . .she entered during spring break 1 995
