But you gotta admire my restraint.

11:34.200 --> 11:37.909
Oh, come on, look how much you've
accomplished since we've been together.

11:38.080 --> 11:41.038
You're exercising regularly,
you cut way down on the drinking. . .

11:41.200 --> 11:42.599
. . .and you're eating right.

11:42.760 --> 11:45.672
Did you ever think you'd
change your life the way you have?

11:45.840 --> 11:47.353
Never.

11:48.680 --> 11:51.797
lt just goes to show, you can do
anything you put your mind to.

11:56.120 --> 11:57.917
l smell meat.

11:58.800 --> 11:59.789
Excuse me?

12:00.280 --> 12:02.555
Your breath. lt stinks of meat.

12:04.680 --> 12:07.990
Well, it could be my tongue.

12:08.200 --> 12:09.713
My tongue is meat.

12:09.880 --> 12:12.474
No, you've been eating meat.
l can smell it.

12:14.320 --> 12:17.630
Maybe it's this breast of Tofurky
you smell.

12:18.200 --> 12:21.590
-No, l smell beef.
-Where would l get beef?

12:21.760 --> 12:22.875
You tell me.

12:23.600 --> 12:26.592
Well, maybe it's secondhand beef.

12:27.000 --> 12:29.992
-What?
-You know, like secondhand smoke.

12:30.160 --> 12:31.354
Some thoughtless guy. . .

12:31.520 --> 12:34.398
. . .who's sitting next to you
eating a steak can--

12:37.000 --> 12:39.150
Oh, screw it.

12:40.160 --> 12:43.311
l paid a slightly disturbed woman
to toss a bag of cheeseburgers. . .

12:43.480 --> 12:45.675
. . .onto the deck
while you were getting dressed.

12:46.280 --> 12:50.831
-Oh, Charlie.
-Don't ''Oh, Charlie'' me, l was starving.

12:51.000 --> 12:53.230
And l'll tell you another thing,
my power walk. . .

12:53.400 --> 12:57.518
. . .was two quick beers and half a Cuban
cigar while cowering in my own garage.

12:57.680 --> 12:59.477
That's why you smelt like
Lemon Pledge.

12:59.640 --> 13:03.076
Well, it certainly wasn't to bring out
the natural luster of my forehead.

13:03.240 --> 13:04.514
So you've been lying to me?

13:05.000 --> 13:08.037
lf you mean telling you
l wasn't going to do a bunch of things. . .

13:08.200 --> 13:12.193
. . .then doing them anyway and lying
about it, then l've been lying to you.

13:13.440 --> 13:17.399
Well, l suppose l can forgive you.
lf you promise it'll never happen again.

13:17.560 --> 13:19.596
Oh, it'll never happen again.
You know why?

13:19.760 --> 13:22.638
Because l am done
with this whole charade.

13:22.800 --> 13:25.792
l'm tired of you trying
to make me over into something l'm not.

13:25.960 --> 13:27.837
l'm a grown man,
not a work in progress.

13:28.000 --> 13:30.195
-Charlie, people are staring.
-Let them stare.

13:31.160 --> 13:32.559
You guys know what l mean.

13:32.720 --> 13:34.950
