with the word ''curd'' in it.

13:51.120 --> 13:53.190
You know,
you're turning into a real ass here.

13:53.360 --> 13:56.193
Well,
then l'm finally living up to my potential.

13:56.760 --> 13:59.797
l'm a big old bourbon-soaked,
cigar-huffing ass. . .

13:59.960 --> 14:02.394
. . .as God, in his infinite wisdom,
meant me to be.

14:02.560 --> 14:04.471
As he meant all men to be.

14:14.080 --> 14:17.072
You guys are disappointing God.

14:20.800 --> 14:24.076
Okay,
what if a cannibal was on death row?

14:24.480 --> 14:26.277
l guess for being a cannibal.

14:26.960 --> 14:31.112
