15:41.080 --> 15:43.878
l didn't mean dump her,
l meant grow a pair.

15:46.280 --> 15:47.838
What is ''whipped''?

15:48.000 --> 15:51.072
When a man lets a woman take over
his life and tell him what to do.

15:51.240 --> 15:53.151
Oh, so like you and Mom.

15:56.680 --> 15:57.669
No.

16:02.320 --> 16:04.151
Oh, hi, Mother.

16:04.320 --> 16:06.914
No, no, Mia's not here.
He broke up with her.

16:07.680 --> 16:10.592
Yeah, schmuck seems to be
the general consensus.

16:11.280 --> 16:13.953
-What's a ''schmuck''?
-Any guy who's not whipped.

16:14.120 --> 16:17.157
-She wants to talk to you.
-Well, l don't wanna talk to her.

16:17.720 --> 16:19.073
Nice catch, schmuck.

16:24.000 --> 16:25.194
Hi, Mom.

16:27.280 --> 16:29.794
Why am l the bad guy here?

16:29.960 --> 16:33.714
Well, did you ever stop to consider
that maybe this wasn't my fault?

16:33.880 --> 16:36.030
l gotta go, Mom,
my meat connection's here.

16:39.360 --> 16:43.558
lt's just weird. l just think that if the guy's
got a front door, we should use it.

16:43.720 --> 16:45.517
-This is fine.
-Okay.

16:45.680 --> 16:48.433
-Hi, Charlie.
-Hello, Rose. What's going on?

16:49.080 --> 16:52.914
Well, l just wanted to introduce you
to Gordon, my new boyfriend.

16:53.360 --> 16:56.079
Oh, no kidding. Hi, Gordon.

16:56.240 --> 16:57.355
Hello.

16:57.520 --> 17:00.114
Gordon and l
are in a committed relationship.

17:00.280 --> 17:01.759
